<body>

    <div class="container mt-2">
        <!-- Title Section -->
        <h1 class="text-center mb-2">Flight Booking System Guidelines</h1>
        
        <!-- Guidelines List -->
        <div class="card shadow p-4">
            <ol class="list-group list-group-numbered">
                <!-- Guideline 1 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Accurate Information Entry:</strong> 
                    Ensure all passenger details (name, date of birth, passport number) are entered correctly to avoid issues at the airport.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 2 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Valid Identification Documents:</strong> 
                    Passengers must carry a valid passport or government-issued ID during check-in.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 3 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Flight Selection and Confirmation:</strong> 
                    Review flight details carefully before confirming the booking. Double-check the date, time, and destination.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 4 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Payment Security:</strong> 
                    Use secure payment gateways and avoid sharing sensitive payment information with unauthorized sources.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 5 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Cancellation and Refund Policy:</strong> 
                    Familiarize yourself with the cancellation and refund policies of the airline before booking.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 6 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Check-In Process:</strong> 
                    Complete online check-in if available to save time at the airport.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 7 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Baggage Allowance:</strong> 
                    Adhere to the airline’s baggage policies to avoid extra charges.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 8 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Travel Insurance:</strong> 
                    Consider purchasing travel insurance to cover unforeseen circumstances.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 9 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Flight Updates:</strong> 
                    Keep track of flight status updates for any changes in schedule.
                </li>
                
                <!-- Guideline 10 -->
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>Customer Support:</strong> 
                    Reach out to the airline’s customer support for assistance if you face any issues during booking.
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>